description: The 3D Printing Club is established for the purpose of educating UF students on the world of 3D printing and how 3D printing and related skills can be used within their education, professionally, and leisurely. Additionally, projects will be set in place to address issues seen within the University of Florida, the local Gainesville area, and nationally.
